item.title: CVE-2023-2776|2024-08-02T06:33:05.772Z -- code-projects -- simple%20photo%20gallery
item.description: A vulnerability was found in code-projects Simple Photo Gallery 1.0. It has been declared as critical. This vulnerability affects unknown code. The manipulation leads to unrestricted upload. The attack can be initiated remotely. VDB-229282 is the identifier assigned to this vulnerability.
